request_text: Deposit to asset ratio by bank region

policy_decision.reason: Low sensitivity data allowed for all authenticated roles

sql.final_sql: SELECT bank_region, AVG(deposit_to_asset_ratio) AS deposit_to_asset_ratio_avg FROM dp_call_reports WHERE 1=1 GROUP BY bank_region HAVING COUNT(*) >= 10 ORDER BY bank_region
sql.canonical_sql: SELECT BANK_REGION, AVG(DEPOSIT_TO_ASSET_RATIO) AS DEPOSIT_TO_ASSET_RATIO_AVG FROM DP_CALL_REPORTS WHERE 1=1 GROUP BY BANK_REGION HAVING COUNT(*) >= 10 ORDER BY BANK_REGION
